## Quality

- Read before editing. No partial implementations. Verify before reporting done.
- `/validate` is the **Pipeline Gate** before every commit. The pre-commit hook checks for a `.validation_passed` sentinel (created by `/validate`, deleted on any file edit). Missing sentinel → commit blocked. See `.claude/rules/validation-loop.md`.
- If unsure, say so explicitly — never guess silently.

